<style>
@@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800;900&display=swap');

#Say {
    width: 100%;
    background: #040814;
    padding: 100px 32px;
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
}

#Say::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    width: 500px; height: 500px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(0,196,168,0.06) 0%, transparent 70%);
    border-radius: 50%;
    top: -150px; right: -150px;
    pointer-events: none;
}

.say-inner {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
}

.say-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 56px;
}

.say-label {
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 700;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: #00c4a8;
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 14px;
}

.say-label::before,
.say-label::after {
    content: '';
    display: inline-block;
    width: 24px; height: 2px;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #00c4a8, #0ea5e9);
    border-radius: 2px;
}

.say-header h2 {
    font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 42px);
    font-weight: 800;
    color: #f8fafc;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
}

/* Cards grid */
.say-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fill, minmax(320px, 1fr));
    gap: 24px;
}

.say-card {
    background: rgba(255,255,255,0.03);
    border: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
    border-radius: 20px;
    padding: 32px;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    position: relative;
}

.say-card:hover {
    background: rgba(0,196,168,0.04);
    border-color: rgba(0,196,168,0.18);
    transform: translateY(-5px);
    box-shadow: 0 20px 50px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
}

.say-quote-icon {
    font-size: 32px;
    color: rgba(0,196,168,0.25);
    margin-bottom: 18px;
    display: block;
}

.say-card p {
    font-size: 14.5px;
    color: rgba(203,213,225,0.7);
    line-height: 1.75;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    font-style: italic;
}

.say-stars {
    display: flex;
    gap: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
}

.say-stars i {
    color: #fbbf24;
    font-size: 13px;
}

.say-author {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    padding-top: 20px;
    border-top: 1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
}

.say-author-img {
    width: 48px; height: 48px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    object-fit: cover;
    border: 2px solid rgba(0,196,168,0.3);
}

.say-author-info h4 {
    font-size: 15px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f8fafc;
    margin-bottom: 2px;
}

.say-author-info span {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #00c4a8;
    font-weight: 500;
}

@@media (max-width: 768px) {
    #Say { padding: 70px 20px; }
    .say-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
}
</style>

<section id="Say">
    <div class="say-inner">
        <div class="say-header">
            <span class="say-label">What They Say</span>
            <h2>Student Testimonials</h2>
        </div>

        <div class="say-grid">
            <div class="say-card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left say-quote-icon"></i>
                <div class="say-stars">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                </div>
                <p>"Choosing online studies was the best way to do it – the internet is fast, cheap & popular and it's easy to communicate in social media with native speakers."</p>
                <div class="say-author">
                    <img src="~/assets/images/testimonials.jpg" alt="Nina Farel" class="say-author-img">
                    <div class="say-author-info">
                        <h4>Nina Farel</h4>
                        <span>@@shamsadfg</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="say-card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left say-quote-icon"></i>
                <div class="say-stars">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star-half-stroke"></i>
                </div>
                <p>"The course content is absolutely amazing. I learned more in 2 weeks here than in months of traditional studying. The instructors are world-class!"</p>
                <div class="say-author">
                    <img src="~/assets/images/testimonials.jpg" alt="Nina Farel" class="say-author-img">
                    <div class="say-author-info">
                        <h4>Alex Johnson</h4>
                        <span>@@alexj_dev</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="say-card">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-quote-left say-quote-icon"></i>
                <div class="say-stars">
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i><i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                    <i class="fa-solid fa-star"></i>
                </div>
                <p>"This platform changed my career. The practical projects and mentorship helped me land my dream job. I highly recommend it to anyone looking to grow."</p>
                <div class="say-author">
                    <img src="~/assets/images/testimonials.jpg" alt="Sara M" class="say-author-img">
                    <div class="say-author-info">
                        <h4>Sara Mitchell</h4>
                        <span>@@sara_codes</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
